{"tid":1980159,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"轉載~清算師有關開Twitter之教學","createTime":"2020-04-20T02:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T07:09:17.000Z","uid":267730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b615d8ccb0d2e109f6d9aaeb07786db8873bd5","tid":1980159,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pwTHY7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pwTHY7.jpg&h=aeeb5f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前日早上，政權大舉圍捕民主派人士，以公安條例大舉作出政治檢控。尋晚林鄭政府赤裸裸地放棄根據基本法治港，管治實權正式移交中聯辦。就呢兩件事件而言，大家而家可以做既就係話比全世界人知，港共政權係抗疫關鍵時期仍不忘打壓人櫂自由。<br />\n<br />\n大家都應該聽過，外國大部分人主要用Twitter，要有效廣傳消息一定要靠佢。以下簡單幾步，希望大家一齊幫下手，需時約15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n＜事前準備＞ (需時3-5分鐘)<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter<br />\n呢樣唔駛多講，Twitter下以用電話[手動打+852]或email註冊，網址係 <a href=\"https://twitter.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPuCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=24306316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com</a>。係[你地興趣]果頁打HongKong就會預設一堆人比你follow。<br />\n<br />\n2. 再Follow多d人+出兩條tweet<br />\n同其他社交媒體一樣，乜都用既account可能會被當電腦。搵人Follow既小祕訣係Search bar打 #StandWithHongKong 再揀人物，就可以搵到哂做緊同樣野既戰友，Follow哂佢地啦。同樣地可以Search其他字眼搵多d人follow。之後右下藍圈[+]制打兩篇Tweet，內容乜都得，幾個字就可以，咁事前準備就完成。<br />\n<br />\n＜衝出國際＞ (需時5-10分鐘)<br />\n1. 大家平時見到話邊個外國議員出Tweet支持香港，邊個政府譴責港共打壓人權，呢d資料係邊度搵到呢？同大家介紹兩個小工具。<br />\n(a) 香城Online App (<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPuCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=f0701a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a>)<br />\n呢個App每日都會搜集各國名人討論香港既Tweet，入到去揀&quot;任務欄&quot;就會睇到。今日當然全部都係尋日兩件大事啦。<br />\n(b) Telegram<br />\n有用Telegram既可以去 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPuCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=9dcb784c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> ，揀/task就會有唔同類型既Tweet選擇。<br />\n<br />\n2. Retweet 同埋 Comment<br />\n(a) Retweet (重要)<br />\n入到條Tweet到見到有兩個打圈箭咀粒掣就係Retweet，之後揀Retweet就完成，Comment果度會分開做。<br />\n(b) Comment<br />\nRetweet左邊果粒bubble掣就係Comment，督入去係咁意打幾隻字感想，內容諗唔到可以參考其他人(但唔係copy and paste，會當你係電腦)。內容記住要有&quot;Hong Kong&quot;兩隻字！<br />\n上面果兩個平台應該有好多Tweet要大家幫手，呢個步驟不停重複就可以。<br />\n<br />\n＜完成！＞<br />\n上面兩個渠道都有大量Tweet要大家Retweet with comment，希望大家習慣每日搭車番屋企時都花10分鐘入去做下任務啦！(註：香港晚上係歐洲下午/美國清晨時份，所以大家放工時間推Post最有效Share去全世界)<br />\n<br />\n呢個Post有d長，多謝大家睇哂！"},{"pid":"ae2f04919712bcb65598e7161ba9d6073263d99f","tid":1980159,"uid":306681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0753f2b33bf585e0a11c0aaa97f295e1b406fd00","tid":1980159,"uid":306681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:11:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fa70860228863b333e30d68b542deb105a9f7af","tid":1980159,"uid":306681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea1c5b8e16928df0d2be026f3bb8e050623a46d8","tid":1980159,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPuCCrfoqRshWq79J%2FX5JLMA%3D&h=9dcb784c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n仲有拉到最底有twitter collection<br />\n用browser開一次過搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"h